1
00:00:13,480 --> 00:00:14,600
Son of a bitch!

2
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:16,329
To hell with the law!

3
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:18,080
I am the Military Governor,

4
00:00:18,080 --> 00:00:19,210
and I am above it all.

5
00:00:19,640 --> 00:00:20,840
Anyone who talks back

6
00:00:20,840 --> 00:00:21,570
will be shot.

7
00:00:23,520 --> 00:00:24,440
So lively here.

8
00:00:27,640 --> 00:00:28,280
Madam.

9
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:29,360
Madam.

10
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:31,400
You left in such a hurry,

11
00:00:31,400 --> 00:00:32,800
without even waiting for me.

12
00:00:32,800 --> 00:00:33,600
Do you want to die?

13
00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:34,200
Madam.

14
00:00:34,400 --> 00:00:35,520
I'm already late.

15
00:00:35,800 --> 00:00:36,600
You have no idea.

16
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:37,680
In this little Taohua Town,

17
00:00:37,680 --> 00:00:38,360
there is actually someone

18
00:00:38,360 --> 00:00:40,520
who doesn't respect this Military Governor.

19
00:00:40,520 --> 00:00:41,600
Is that so?

20
00:00:42,440 --> 00:00:43,640
I'd like to see

21
00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:45,200
who has the nerve.

22
00:00:45,680 --> 00:00:47,000
Don't they know you're the Marshal's brother-in-law?

23
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:48,120
Yes, Madam.

24
00:00:48,840 --> 00:00:49,720
It's this kid.

25
00:00:57,320 --> 00:00:58,080
I'm useless.

26
00:00:58,200 --> 00:00:59,530
I disgraced you, Madam.

27
00:01:00,040 --> 00:01:01,300
Hurry up and shoot him!

28
00:01:01,320 --> 00:01:02,280
Look how angry Madam is.

29
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:03,200
Who dares!

30
00:01:09,520 --> 00:01:10,050
Let's go.

31
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:12,280
Wait a minute.

32
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:17,280
Madam.

33
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:18,860
What are you doing?

34
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:22,440
What's going on?

35
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:23,970
The Governor's wife

36
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:25,480
knows Brother Wang?

37
00:01:25,880 --> 00:01:26,920
This damned executioner

38
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:29,120
actually has an affair with the Governor's wife?

39
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:31,050
You've got some nerve, Wang Shiqi.

40
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,360
My son

41
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,330
died just like this?

42
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:38,000
So what if he died?

43
00:01:38,880 --> 00:01:40,400
It's better than making Madam angry.

44
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,600
It's good that I died.

45
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:43,759
Don't do this.

46
00:01:45,759 --> 00:01:47,020
Sister, don't do this.

47
00:01:47,600 --> 00:01:48,600
Don't do this, sister.

48
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:49,800
I can't take it.

49
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:50,880
I...

50
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:52,610
I really can't take it, sister.

51
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:53,680
Sister.

52
00:01:55,240 --> 00:01:55,840
What?

53
00:01:56,039 --> 00:01:57,320
Don't you remember me?

54
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,640
I remember.

55
00:01:58,640 --> 00:01:59,440
Of course I do.

56
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,130
At that time,

57
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:02,900
my father knew you were a hero.

58
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:03,480
So,

59
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:05,000
he put on such a big show

60
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:07,210
to help you fake your death and escape.

61
00:02:07,440 --> 00:02:07,760
This...

62
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:08,889
It hasn't been long.

63
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:10,259
I didn't expect

64
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:12,180
you'd become the Warlord's wife.

65
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:16,210
The great kindness of you and your father,

66
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:18,050
I will never forget.

67
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,000
By the way,

68
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:21,660
what exactly happened

69
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:23,320
to make our good-tempered Warlord

70
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:24,320
want to shoot you?

71
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,360
This Warlord

72
00:02:29,920 --> 00:02:32,180
probably only has a good temper with you.

73
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,640
I can't believe this happened.

74
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:39,640
It's outrageous.

75
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:41,450
Don't worry.

76
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:43,920
I'll make sure the Warlord investigates everything.

77
00:02:43,920 --> 00:02:45,400
If the evidence is conclusive,

78
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:47,730
even if Song Ping is the Warlord's cousin,

79
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:50,200
I will not let him off easily.

80
00:02:50,640 --> 00:02:51,700
Thank you, Sister.

81
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:52,900
Thank you, Sister.

82
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,480
My son.

83
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:57,440
Don't worry.

84
00:02:58,440 --> 00:02:59,900
I have begged our ancestor

85
00:03:00,160 --> 00:03:01,890
to grant another magic weapon.

86
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:03,880
I will definitely make Wang Shiqi

87
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:05,760
pay with his life.

88
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:40,440
Please.

89
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:43,440
Have a seat, Madam.

90
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,329
To show my sincerity...

91
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:48,760
I specially set up this banquet

92
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:49,840
to entertain the Warlord

93
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:50,700
and you, Madam.

94
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,780
This mansion is so luxurious.

95
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:57,920
It seems you've extorted a lot from the people.

96
00:04:01,320 --> 00:04:03,180
You are absolutely right, Madam.

97
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:09,240
Come.

98
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:09,680
Madam.

99
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:10,360
Come.

100
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:13,080
Madam.

101
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:22,320
I heard

102
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:25,460
you've done a lot of 'good deeds' in Taohua Town.

103
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,160
Answer whatever

104
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:30,260
Madam asks you.

105
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:33,320
Madam,

106
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:36,240
don't listen to Wang Shiqi's nonsense.

107
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:37,720
He is a man

108
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,320
of unknown origin.

109
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,520
To please Su Wanrong

110
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:42,600
and Mayor Su,

111
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,400
he deliberately targets me.

112
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,400
You know what?

113
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:47,360
They set a trap

114
00:04:47,440 --> 00:04:48,800
and killed my son.

115
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:51,840
My son died an unjust death.

116
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,480
Yes, Madam.

117
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:58,100
How come I didn't know he was this kind of person?

118
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:02,120
Madam,

119
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,880
are you very familiar with Wang Shiqi?

120
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:05,680
Yes, Madam.

121
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,450
What exactly is going on

122
00:05:07,520 --> 00:05:09,450
between you and that executioner?

123
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:15,170
I am here to have you ask the questions.

124
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:18,320
What do you mean by questioning me instead?

125
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:24,840
You must figure out everything tonight

126
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:28,580
and give an explanation to all the townsfolk tomorrow.

127
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:30,480
Madam.

128
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:32,200
Aren't you going to eat more?

129
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:34,730
Disgusting.

130
00:05:35,280 --> 00:05:36,340
I have no appetite.

131
00:05:41,320 --> 00:05:42,159
Uncle,

132
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:43,480
you saw it too.

133
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:46,460
It's not that I don't care about family ties.

134
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:49,440
It's just that I have to listen to Madam.

135
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:50,740
You're on your own.

136
00:05:55,080 --> 00:05:55,920
Commander,

137
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:59,760
Madam's relationship with Wang Shiqi

138
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:01,720
is not simple.

139
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:07,120
What do you mean

140
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:08,800
by that?

141
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:10,400
As far as I know,

142
00:06:11,200 --> 00:06:12,530
Madam and the Commander

143
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:15,250
have been married for seven years, right?

144
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:17,160
Be careful,

145
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:19,400
the new always replaces the old.

146
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:26,000
This old man

147
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:28,280
actually suspects Shiqi and me.

148
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,120
It's ridiculous.

149
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:38,520
However,

150
00:06:39,400 --> 00:06:42,000
Shiqi does seem to have become more handsome

151
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:44,320
and stronger.
